trans-unit.source: Represents an ordered collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa una colección ordenada de objetos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding" />.

trans-unit.source: All objects that derive from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> have an <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBindingCollection> named <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.InputBindings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Todos los objetos que derivan de <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> tiene un <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBindingCollection> denominado <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.InputBindings%2A>.

trans-unit.source: All objects that derive from <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement> have an <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBindingCollection> named <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.InputBindings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Todos los objetos que derivan de <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement> tiene un <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBindingCollection> denominado <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.InputBindings%2A>.

trans-unit.source: However, if these collections are set in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], then the items in the collection must be derived classes of <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> rather than direct <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> objects.
trans-unit.target: Sin embargo, si estas colecciones se establecen [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], a continuación, los elementos de la colección deben ser clases derivadas de <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> en lugar de direct <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> objetos.

trans-unit.source: This is because <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> does not support a default public constructor.
trans-unit.target: Esto es porque <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> no admite un constructor público predeterminado.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, the items in a <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBindingCollection> that was set in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] will typically be an <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> derived class that does support a default public constructor, such as <xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyBinding> or <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding>.
trans-unit.target: Por lo tanto, los elementos de un <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBindingCollection> que se estableció [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] normalmente será un <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> clase derivada que admite un constructor público predeterminado, como <xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyBinding> o <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding>.

trans-unit.target: Solo se puede utilizar cuando la instancia de <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBindingCollection> se convierte en una interfaz <xref:System.Collections.IList>.
